.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F153901_bd2dbc96e502ed7422285a41aa1f5421.jpg&h=622a5c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/153906_1f0644f03a859f3b18faa3d4a849366d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F153906_1f0644f03a859f3b18faa3d4a849366d.jpg&h=ab044cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手係另一個POST<br />\n佢自爆約左好多個連登仔出黎<br />\n比其中一個連登仔性騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>[認真長文]4月頭同左某波台會員出黎，好不愉快</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/644940/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/644940/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲不停自貼腳話自己腳唔粗 好索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫人唔好貼佢樣 貼多啲佢腳圖 (曲線想自爆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/154156_a170f9d68cf564554e02cabc05d05dd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F154156_a170f9d68cf564554e02cabc05d05dd4.jpg&h=476a1c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/154551_1a9e5191b24bd1dd42a9d0ec21ed3ca8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F154551_1a9e5191b24bd1dd42a9d0ec21ed3ca8.jpg&h=d736dbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得果160係咁強調自己隻蘿蔔腳唔粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq